Dunst Configuration
===================

The directory contains a [`dunstrc`](./dunstrc) file which contains the
configuration of `dunst` program.

It also contains two png file which are used as icons for
    - normal notification
    - urgent notification

The [`setup`](./setup) file is script for automation (which makes lyf
easy).

Want sound with notification?
-----------------------------

There section `[play_sound]` at the last of [`dunstrc`](./dunstrc).

What you should do for sound to play correctly:

    1. Make sure the audio file does not contains any image in metadata
    1. Only absolute path to the script works
    1. And, yes it could be a script or an audio file
